## 🎨 **Design Requirements**

### **🎯 User Experience Goals**
- **Data-Driven**: Clear and actionable insights
- **Interactive**: Engaging data visualization
- **Comprehensive**: Complete coverage of all metrics
- **Customizable**: Tailored views and reports
- **Mobile-Friendly**: Accessible on all devices

### **🔧 Technical Requirements**
- **Responsive Design**: Works on desktop, tablet, and mobile
- **Accessibility**: WCAG 2.1 AAA compliant
- **Performance**: Fast data loading and rendering
- **Integration**: Real-time data from all modules
- **Security**: Secure access to sensitive data

